    "Considerations": [
        "During system updates or patches, legitimate modifications to registry keys related to port monitors might occur. These changes are part of the update process and should be verified before raising an alert.",
        "When new printer drivers are installed or existing ones are updated, they may modify registry keys under 'SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Print\\Monitors'. These modifications are expected and should be cross-checked with recent administrative activities.",
        "Administrators performing routine maintenance tasks might modify registry settings related to port monitors. Such activities should be verified against scheduled maintenance logs to rule out false positives."
